msgstr "RET @r{(Buffer Menu)}"

#. type: table
#: original_texis/buffers.texi:460
msgid ""
"Select this line's buffer, replacing the @file{*Buffer List*} buffer in its "
"window (@code{Buffer-menu-this-window})."
